-Title- 
Venus secures Muguruza rematch at WTA Finals
-Keywords-
['wta', 'group', 'pool', 'pliskova', 'muguruza', 'wimbledon', 'rematch', 'venus', 'finals', 'garcia', 'secures', 'final', 'williams']
