-Title- 
U.S. fund investors regain risk appetite as Dow breaches 23,000
-Keywords-
['week', 'dow', 'lipper', '23000', 'investors', 'appetite', 'breaches', 'york', 'billion', 'fund', 'growth', 'risk', 'funds', 'posted', 'stock', 'regain', 'according', 'outflows']
