-Title- 
Having nuclear weapons 'matter of life and death' for N.Korea - agency
-Keywords-
['united', 'weapons', 'washington', 'agency', 'north', 'koreas', 'death', 'korea', 'life', 'nuclear', 'military', 'having', 'matter', 'korean', 'nkorea', 'leader']
