-Title- 
Pair of mosque attacks kill at least 50 in Afghanistan
-Keywords-
['kabul', 'mosque', '50', 'security', 'killed', 'official', 'afghanistan', 'pair', 'bombing', 'attacks', 'attack', 'ghor', 'shiite', 'kill']
