-Title- 
UK business minister travels to Canada for talks on Bombardier deal
-Keywords-
['minister', 'airbus', 'dispute', 'british', 'talks', 'canada', 'business', 'trade', 'cseries', 'northern', 'uk', 'series', 'bombardier', 'deal', 'travels', 'stake']
