-Title- 
Low pay, no bonus: U.S. retailers struggle with hiring
-Keywords-
['retailers', 'hire', 'bonus', 'seasonal', 'pay', 'stores', 'low', 'paid', 'hiring', 'struggle', 'employees', 'job', 'retail', 'bonuses', 'say']
