-Title- 
Exchange podcast: Ruchir Sharma
-Keywords-
['strategist', 'thrive', 'nations', 'ticks', 'podcast', 'metrics', 'place', 'morgan', 'ruchir', 'rise', 'sharma', 'stanley', 'exchange', 'world']
-SUMMARY ARTICLE-
Want to know which emerging markets will thrive and which will fail?
