ROUGH CUT (NO REPORTER NARRATION) STORY: Famous artist Jan Fabre brings his fresh show "Belgian Rules/Belgium Rules" to Moscow - his Antwerp theater's first gig in Russia since 2009.
Belgium is like Russia," Fabre said.
We are bigger than China, bigger than Russia, bigger than America.
