-Title- 
Trump tax cuts gain momentum as Rand Paul goes 'all in'
-Keywords-
['cuts', 'goes', 'senator', 'vote', 'tax', 'senate', 'republican', 'house', 'gain', 'paul', 'rand', 'budget', 'momentum', 'trump']
-SUMMARY ARTICLE-
