-Title- 
Viewsroom: U.S. election, European banks, Uber-Didi
-Keywords-
['opposition', 'needs', 'lenders', 'infrastructure', 'banks', 'uberdidi', 'uber', 'european', 'test', 'election', 'viewsroom', 'stress', 'ups', 'ridesharing', 'trump']
-SUMMARY ARTICLE-
Hillary Clinton and Donald Trump battle over infrastructure needs, while Trump faces growing opposition from fellow billionaires.
Also: the ups and downs of Europe’s lenders after a stress test with no fail grade, and why Uber is ceding to Didi the ride-sharing crown in China.
-TEXT INSIDE ARTICLE-
