-Title- 
Three police officers killed, eight injured in shoot-out in Giza: security sources
-Keywords-
['shootout', 'group', 'islamist', 'insurgency', 'injured', 'security', 'hasm', 'killed', 'suspected', 'brotherhood', 'militant', 'officers', 'giza', 'policemen', 'sources', 'muslim']
