-Title- 
Obama blasts 'politics of division' on return to campaign trail
-Keywords-
['division', 'trail', 'obama', 'politics', 'president', 'white', 'blasts', 'return', 'elections', 'republican', 'house', 'jersey', 'virginia', 'campaign', 'trump']
