“Mounie will be back in the squad. He trained all week without any issues,” Wagner said of the club’s record signing, who has scored twice in the league so far.

Mounie’s attack partner Collin Quaner (calf strain) will miss the United game but could return for next week’s trip to Liverpool while midfielder Kasey Palmer (hamstring) is expected back after next month’s international break.

